John Clarkson from Mr Eaters Fish and Chips in Preston has created 'Pie-egg-ra' The dish contains one and a half Cadbury's Creme Eggs and is served with a side of chips . 
  Mr Clarkson blind-bakes the pastry before the eggs are battered and deep fried . 
  He says customers have taken to dipping chips in the yolk like toast soldiers . 
 